WEBVTT

00:00:00.140 --> 00:00:03.060
=The Crow Princess of Fortune=

00:00:03.060 --> 00:00:04.980
=Episode 26=

00:00:08.060 --> 00:00:09.859
Let's end today's flower banquet here.

00:00:09.860 --> 00:00:11.020
I am tired.

00:00:11.780 --> 00:00:14.699
- Farewell, Father.
- Farewell, Your Majesty.

00:00:14.700 --> 00:00:16.379
Help!

00:00:16.380 --> 00:00:18.019
Help!

00:00:18.020 --> 00:00:19.400
Murder!

00:00:22.580 --> 00:00:23.499
Your Majesty,

00:00:23.500 --> 00:00:24.300
Wu Wang?

00:00:24.340 --> 00:00:25.940
What happened to you?

00:00:26.180 --> 00:00:27.099
Your Majesty, save me!

00:00:27.100 --> 00:00:28.140
Save me quickly!

00:00:28.380 --> 00:00:29.579
No!

00:00:29.580 --> 00:00:31.620
Imperial Preceptor, what happened?

00:00:31.820 --> 00:00:32.499
No!

00:00:32.500 --> 00:00:32.819
No!

00:00:32.820 --> 00:00:33.940
Save me quickly!

00:00:35.140 --> 00:00:36.100
Your Highness!

00:00:40.020 --> 00:00:41.259
Your Highness, save me!

00:00:41.260 --> 00:00:42.059
Save me!

00:00:42.060 --> 00:00:43.619
Someone is trying to kill me!

00:00:43.620 --> 00:00:44.419
And snakes!

00:00:44.420 --> 00:00:45.660
There are snakes chasing me!

00:00:46.100 --> 00:00:47.340
Let go!

00:00:58.460 --> 00:01:00.779
Mother?

00:01:00.780 --> 00:01:01.579
This...

00:01:01.580 --> 00:01:02.700
Consort Shu,

00:01:02.780 --> 00:01:04.100
what is this?

00:01:06.040 --> 00:01:07.000
(Family Letter)

00:01:09.020 --> 00:01:10.299
Grandfather,

00:01:10.300 --> 00:01:13.779
the Imperial Preceptor used puppet
talismans to control Crown Prince

00:01:13.780 --> 00:01:15.179
and tried to harm my Father.

00:01:15.180 --> 00:01:18.899
He also put a slow-acting poison
in your sachet

00:01:18.900 --> 00:01:21.820
to slowly destroy your dragon aura.

00:01:21.900 --> 00:01:24.179
He colluded with Consort Shu

00:01:24.180 --> 00:01:26.419
to place Crown Prince on the throne

00:01:26.420 --> 00:01:27.979
and rule the court themselves.

00:01:27.980 --> 00:01:29.419
All this information,

00:01:29.420 --> 00:01:31.420
Grandfather, you can
investigate yourself.

00:01:33.980 --> 00:01:34.860
Father,

00:01:35.580 --> 00:01:36.179
I

00:01:36.180 --> 00:01:38.700
know nothing about this.

00:01:39.180 --> 00:01:40.220
Your Highness,

00:01:41.100 --> 00:01:42.140
Wu Wang,

00:01:42.860 --> 00:01:44.500
what do you have to say for yourself?

00:01:44.540 --> 00:01:45.780
Your Majesty, I...

00:01:45.980 --> 00:01:48.019
Still refusing to tell the truth?

00:01:48.020 --> 00:01:49.379
Snake, go.

00:01:49.380 --> 00:01:50.299
Bite him.

00:01:50.300 --> 00:01:51.780
Give him some truth venom.

00:01:51.980 --> 00:01:53.459
No!

00:01:53.460 --> 00:01:56.820
Ouch!

00:02:03.380 --> 00:02:05.700
Your Majesty, I am guilty!

00:02:07.860 --> 00:02:09.300
I...

00:02:09.380 --> 00:02:12.420
I had an illicit affair with Consort Shu

00:02:12.540 --> 00:02:14.299
and we had a child together.

00:02:14.300 --> 00:02:16.200
Xiao Jing is the child
between her and me.

00:02:17.000 --> 00:02:18.840
I never expected this.
This is a huge scandal!

00:02:18.840 --> 00:02:19.780
Consort Shu

00:02:19.980 --> 00:02:21.479
used a dead infant back then

00:02:21.480 --> 00:02:23.979
to swap away the Empress's child.

00:02:23.980 --> 00:02:25.300
Actually, Xiao Heng

00:02:25.540 --> 00:02:28.220
is the true legitimate prince.

00:02:32.020 --> 00:02:36.659
I also altered Xiao Heng's fortune,

00:02:36.660 --> 00:02:39.100
causing his defeat in battle
and crippling his leg.

00:02:39.140 --> 00:02:40.859
I created evil formations

00:02:40.860 --> 00:02:42.179
and harmed innocent lives.

00:02:42.180 --> 00:02:44.900
Every single thing was done by me!

00:02:45.980 --> 00:02:49.620
Hahaha!

00:02:50.020 --> 00:02:51.099
This is terrifying.

00:02:51.100 --> 00:02:53.379
I... I was deceived
by that wicked woman.

00:02:53.380 --> 00:02:54.819
Consort Shu...

00:02:54.820 --> 00:02:55.659
She...

00:02:55.660 --> 00:02:56.779
It was Consort Shu!

00:02:56.780 --> 00:02:58.440
She ordered me to do it!

00:02:58.440 --> 00:03:00.680
She said as long as I helped
the Crown Prince ascend the throne,

00:03:00.680 --> 00:03:02.280
she would let me
become the Retired Emperor

00:03:02.280 --> 00:03:03.700
and enjoy endless wealth and glory.

00:03:04.460 --> 00:03:05.459
I lost my senses.

00:03:05.460 --> 00:03:08.020
I am guilty!

00:03:12.580 --> 00:03:13.339
No!

00:03:13.340 --> 00:03:14.460
Mother!

00:03:26.980 --> 00:03:28.620
The criminal Shu

00:03:28.860 --> 00:03:30.340
and the Imperial Preceptor Wu Wang

00:03:30.900 --> 00:03:32.780
murdered the late Empress,

00:03:32.900 --> 00:03:34.700
confused the royal bloodline,

00:03:34.860 --> 00:03:36.300
and brought chaos to the inner palace.

00:03:37.580 --> 00:03:39.180
Throw them into prison

00:03:39.300 --> 00:03:40.700
to await punishment!

00:03:46.700 --> 00:03:47.500
No...

00:03:47.980 --> 00:03:49.100
Mother...

00:03:49.700 --> 00:03:51.420
As for Xiao Jing,

00:03:52.220 --> 00:03:53.700
though you are innocent,

00:03:54.100 --> 00:03:55.840
from today onward,

00:03:56.000 --> 00:03:57.880
you are stripped of your status
and reduced to a commoner.

00:04:09.060 --> 00:04:11.059
Evil has met its punishment.

00:04:11.060 --> 00:04:13.580
I didn't even get
the chance to predict it yet.

00:04:14.700 --> 00:04:16.019
Father, hurry and get ready.

00:04:16.020 --> 00:04:17.220
You're about to rise in status.

00:04:17.380 --> 00:04:19.099
I am starving too.

00:04:19.100 --> 00:04:20.139
Let's hurry back

00:04:20.140 --> 00:04:22.379
and have Uncle Shiwan
make braised spare ribs for me.

00:04:22.380 --> 00:04:23.340
Mm.

00:04:32.000 --> 00:04:35.319
♪Little lucky star,
twinkling with a wink at me♪

00:04:35.320 --> 00:04:39.159
♪Every Chinese New Year day brings
the luckiest fortune slip♪

00:04:39.160 --> 00:04:42.679
♪The God of Wealth favors me,
the Matchmaker ties red strings for me♪

00:04:42.680 --> 00:04:45.640
♪With firecrackers going off,
good things keep coming one after another♪

00:04:46.520 --> 00:04:50.159
♪Make a wish on the very first day
of the Chinese New Year♪

00:04:50.160 --> 00:04:53.920
♪By the second day,
my belly's already round♪

00:04:54.000 --> 00:04:57.319
♪Always talking about dieting,
but the chub never disappears♪

00:04:57.320 --> 00:05:01.360
♪Good food brings joy
and happiness every single day♪

00:05:06.960 --> 00:05:10.639
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
every year is filled with joy♪

00:05:10.640 --> 00:05:14.279
♪I'm bringing blessings to everyone♪

00:05:14.280 --> 00:05:17.999
♪Hands clasped together in greeting♪

00:05:18.000 --> 00:05:21.639
♪May every family be sweet and happy♪

00:05:21.640 --> 00:05:25.319
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
may everything go your way♪

00:05:25.320 --> 00:05:27.239
♪Endlessly flowing♪

00:05:27.240 --> 00:05:33.440
♪Good fortune♪